Chambers, 
Attached please find a letter motion to file a reply in support of the Government's motion to preclude the testimony of Dr. 
Ryan Hall. Attached also are the proposed reply brief and exhibit. The Government submits these documents temporarily 
under seal. 
Respectfully submitted, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
New York, New York 10007
